OL,3,CAdvertising regulator 'failing to
OL,4,Cprotect children from gambling
OL,5,Cmarketing'
OL,7,FBy Senior Business and Economics
OL,8,FProducer Jack Abbey
OL,10,FThe Advertising Standards Agency has
OL,11,Fbeen accused by peers of a "continuing
OL,12,Ffailure" to protect children from
OL,13,Fgambling advertising online.
OL,15,FIn a letter seen by ITV News, Peers
OL,16,Ffor Gambling Reform have written to
OL,17,Fthe Gambling Minister expressing their
OL,18,F"serious concerns" around "content
OL,19,Fmarketing", its appeal to children and
OL,20,Fthe lack of action taken against it.
