OL,3,CAdvertising regulator 'failing to
OL,4,Cprotect children from gambling
OL,5,Cmarketing'
OL,7,FIt's a form of social media post where
OL,8,Fcompanies share material online which
OL,9,Fdoesn't explicitly advertise their
OL,10,Fproduct, but which is designed to be
OL,11,Fshareable and often funny.
OL,13,FThis kind of content now makes up half
OL,14,Fof the hundreds of thousands of posts
OL,15,Fmade by gambling firms online each
OL,16,Fyear, and research from the University
OL,17,Fof Bristol has shown it appeals four
OL,18,Ftimes more to children than adults.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
