OL,3,CAdvertising regulator 'failing to
OL,4,Cprotect children from gambling
OL,5,Cmarketing'
OL,7,FIn just one weekend last year, the ten
OL,8,Flargest betting operators generated
OL,9,Fover 20 million views by this form of
OL,10,Fmarketing. The letter argues this is
OL,11,F"one of the most prolific and
OL,12,Feffective forms of gambling
OL,13,Fadvertising in the UK".
OL,15,FThe Committee of Advertising Practice
OL,16,F(CAP) Code prohibits gambling
OL,17,Fmarketing from having a "strong appeal
OL,18,Fto children".
