OL,7,FThe Midnite adverted that the
OL,8,FAdvertising Standards Agency breached
OL,9,Fits rules
OL,11,FIn his letter Lord Foster says
OL,12,Fresearchers and campaigners first
OL,13,Fraised the issue with the ASA in 2019
OL,14,Fand have seen a "pattern of delay"
OL,15,Fever since, despite multiple promises
OL,16,Fto take action and new evidence of the
OL,17,Fimpact of content marketing.
