OL,7,FIn the letter Lord Foster pointed out:
OL,8,F"The University of Bristol alone has
OL,9,Freported over 150 examples of gambling
OL,10,Fcontent marketing to ASA since 2021."
OL,12,FIt comes as the regulator ruled on
OL,13,FWednesday against a piece of content
OL,14,Fmarketing made by a gambling firm for
OL,15,Fthe first time.
OL,17,FA single post by the firm 'Midnite'
OL,18,Fhas been ruled as in breach of the CAP
OL,19,FCode because it features an AI video
OL,20,Fof footballer Trent Alexander-Arnold.
