OL,7,FDr Raffaello Rossi, who first raised
OL,8,Fthe complaint, said: "In my repeated
OL,9,Fdealings with the ASA, it has become
OL,10,Fpainfully clear that they are
OL,11,Fincapable of drawing a clear line
OL,12,Fbetween content marketing and
OL,13,Fadvertising.
OL,15,F"Time and time again, they have
OL,16,Frejected our complaints as 'out of
OL,17,Fremit' ` while in the same breath
OL,18,Finsisting publicly that 'the vast
OL,19,Fmajority of content marketing is in
OL,20,Fremit'."
