OL,7,FIn his letter, Lord Foster calls on
OL,8,Fthe Gambling Minister Baroness
OL,9,FTwycross to intervene.
OL,11,F"Without ministerial leadership,
OL,12,Fchildren and young people will remain
OL,13,Fexposed to forms of gambling
OL,14,Fadvertising that the evidence shows
OL,15,Fare especially harmful, and that the
OL,16,Fregulator has consistently failed to
OL,17,Faddress."
