OL,7,FA spokesperson for the ASA:
OL,8,F"Protecting children from advertising-
OL,9,Frelated harm sits at the heart of our
OL,10,Fwork, and we have strict rules in
OL,11,Fplace to ensure that gambling ads are
OL,12,Fresponsible and are not targeted at
OL,13,Fchildren, or likely to be of strong
OL,14,Fappeal to them.
OL,16,F"Content marketing raises questions
OL,17,Faround jurisdiction and the boundaries
OL,18,Fbetween advertising and editorial
OL,19,Fcontent.
