OL,7,F"Because of uncertainty on whether and
OL,8,Fhow the Advertising Code applies to
OL,9,Fsocial media posts by gambling
OL,10,Foperators who are based abroad, we've
OL,11,Fhad to take time and care to ensure
OL,12,Four regulation covers them effectively.
OL,14,F"The scope of the Advertising Code has
OL,15,Fnow been clarified and extended, which
OL,16,Fwill give us greater room to tackle
OL,17,Fpotentially irresponsible gambling
OL,18,Fads."
